 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3078980a06909943cc12e4f40b94d402dc994dc2","tid":262671,"uid":16539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"異獸戰3:問手無敵 不日上映<br />\n<br />\n故事發展始於90年代初葉問師父到美國發揚詠春時所捲入的一場外星生物大戰。當時葉師父與加洲洲長伸力加正在切砌武藝，向世界宣揚詠春。某日，當葉師父在加洲洲遊時，突然目及正在參加成人禮的鐵血星球的鐵血少年戰士與數十隻異形大戰。葉師父不甘其異形以多取勝，咆哮一聲：「給我來十個」。最終，一套驚世的詠春拳把異形打得落花流水。身負重傷的少年鐵血戰士眼神空洞的看著葉問，此時心中正在盤算著一個陰謀......"},{"pid":"02383ca14c404e7c203de3121bf6be99595ae777","tid":262671,"uid":24141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉問4 打劉馬車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rGFQN7ZYtFI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrGFQN7ZYtFI&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=11d457a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rGFQN7ZYtFI</a>"},{"pid":"23c1b72994400be8d2889873ff73e4531b31bfbe","tid":262671,"uid":29211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"胡師傅"},{"pid":"e8bff06bb0afd73a84a6a72e876b53aa24bfd18d","tid":262671,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/9FebIpraemQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9FebIpraemQ&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b695fc51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9FebIpraemQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇幾次都覺得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=